WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.601 --> 00:00:05.167
man:
The Recommendation gadgets

00:00:05.167 --> 00:00:08.434
let visitors recommend
what they like,

00:00:08.434 --> 00:00:11.868
find the most popular
content,

00:00:11.868 --> 00:00:14.300
see who recommended it,

00:00:14.300 --> 00:00:16.400
and learn more about them.

00:00:18.133 --> 00:00:19.934
This feature is a bit
more advanced

00:00:19.934 --> 00:00:22.701
and you will need to configure
multiple gadgets.

00:00:22.701 --> 00:00:25.968
Start by setting up
the recommendation list.

00:00:25.968 --> 00:00:29.801
You can change the header text,
number of items to show,

00:00:29.801 --> 00:00:32.133
width, and color.

00:00:34.701 --> 00:00:38.934
Then configure the buttons
by choosing the style, icon,

00:00:38.934 --> 00:00:40.901
and button text.

00:00:40.901 --> 00:00:42.801
Click "Generate code"

00:00:42.801 --> 00:00:47.300
and copy the snippets
into the body of your HTML.

00:00:47.300 --> 00:00:50.501
For advanced functionality
such as placing multiple buttons

00:00:50.501 --> 00:00:51.901
on one page,

00:00:51.901 --> 00:00:55.033
you can edit the code snippets
directly.

00:00:55.033 --> 00:00:58.300
Go to google.com/friendconnect
to get started.

